$ GoogleEarth kml: Style element

The following → tools/Google-Earth/kml[kml] example tries to demonstrate the usage of the `<Style>` and `<LineStyle>` elements to color a `<LineString`>:

gh|about-GoogleEarth|/kml/elements/Style/LineStyle.kml||

The result of this kml document:
gh|about-GoogleEarth|/kml/elements/Style/img/LineStyle.png||

sa:
  Using → tools/Google-Earth/kml/elements/Style/styleUrl[`<styleUrl>`] to refer to a predfined `<Style>` from multiple *Geometry* objects.
